62
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:07,830
Bahkan bersama-sama, mereka bukan tandinganku.

63
00:04:08,990 --> 00:04:10,700
Tapi jika saya tidak muncul,

64
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,208
