00:08:34,190 --> 00:08:35,190
Biarkan aku pergi.

134
00:08:35,470 --> 00:08:36,310
aku ingin...

135
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:38,340
Biarkan aku pergi.

136
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:39,500
